    "Description": "We\u2019ve been investigating a recent bout of OD\u2019s and they all seem to have originated with a bad batch of drugs made over at ~mission(Location|Address). \n\nI\u2019m working with other contractors to ferret out those responsible, but people are dying as long is the product is still out there. \n\nI want you to go the site and destroy the stash they have there. Should buy us some time before we shut them down for good.\n\nThey will have guards protecting their supply, so be prepared to engage with hostiles.\n\nCONTRACT AUTHORIZED BY:\nLiaison Officer Bautista\nID# 948J030K",
